txt.en: 'Ah, more mail. Thanks for bringing it by.'

'Hello, friend. Glad to see you here, as I could use your help, if your duties as a Bounder aren't keeping you too busy.\n\n'This is the main messenger office for all the Shire, and as you can imagine, it is quite busy! If, in your rounds, you could drop off a bundle or two, I would appreciate it.'
